      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted on a geometry and operating regime sufficiently similar to the COU device and conditions.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller topology with the COU device. Operating points span the clinically relevant CPB range. Geometric and functional similarity established through dimensional analysis. Achieved level 2 meets requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
