      "rationale": "Independent review of simulation setup is not mandated at MRL 2. Internal review by the analysis team confirmed boundary condition consistency with the experimental protocol. Factor scoped to level 1; acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
