      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity of QoI to turbulence model selection must be quantified through comparison of at least two turbulence model formulations.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required. The SST k-omega model was selected based on literature consensus for rotating machinery hemolysis prediction. Factor not assessed; acceptable at MRL 2."
    },
    {
