    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-cpb-decision-001",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are each demonstrated to be acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met across all 5 evaluated operating points.",
